## This .gitattributes file automatically formats the EOL character in certain filetypes within the repository

## Source code
# JavaScript, TypeScript source files
*.js                    text eol=lf
*.ts                    text eol=lf

# Shell scripts
*.sh                    text eol=lf
*.bash                  text eol=lf

# Windows batch and PowerShell scripts
*.bat                   text eol=crlf
*.cmd                   text eol=crlf
*.ps1                   text eol=crlf

##### Other file types #####

## Text files and documentation
*.txt                   text
*.md                    text diff=markdown
README*                 text
RELEASING*              text
CHANGELOG*              text
CONTRIBUTING*           text
INSTALL*                text
LICENSE*                text

## Non-text documentation
*.html                  text diff=html
*.pdf                   binary
*.json                  text eol=lf
*.rtf                   binary

## Git Properties
.gitignore              text
.gitmodules             text
.gitattributes          text